  "body": "## 50 MRG\n\nAdd two colorway variants sharing base geometry fields where schema allows.\n\n## Acceptance\n\n- [ ] 2 SKUs + tests + notes\n\n\n## Claim (MergeOS MRG)\n\n1. Follow https://github.com/mergeos-bounties\n2. Star https://github.com/mergeos-bounties/mergeos\n3. Star https://github.com/mergeos-bounties/mergeos-contracts\n4. Comment on **this issue**: `I claim this bounty`\n5. Comment on MergeOS [Claim Token #1](https://github.com/mergeos-bounties/mergeos/issues/1) with a link to this issue\n6. Open a PR to **BeeAR** with `Fixes #<this-issue>`\n\nPolicy: [docs/BOUNTY.md](../blob/master/docs/BOUNTY.md)\n\n## Payout\n\nMaintainer reviews PR → merge → **MRG credit** on MergeOS ledger to `github:<author>` (25 / 50 / 100 / 200 scale per labels).\n\n## Evidence\n\nAttach screenshots / sample output / photos as required by acceptance. No secrets, no force-push, no scraped private PII.\n",
